{"tid":2070391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國向加拿大人康明凱及邁克爾提公訴","createTime":"2020-06-19T06:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T06:02:31.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90d2e42e8e37fd6fe281e323eeaa80c59a424105","tid":2070391,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"最高人民檢察院公布，經依法審查，北京市人民檢察院第二分院以涉嫌為境外刺探國家秘密、情報罪，對加拿大籍被告人康明凱提起公訴。此外，檢察機關依法對加拿大人邁克爾涉嫌為境外刺探、非法提供國家秘密案提起公訴。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大2018年12月應美國要求，在溫哥華拘捕正在過境的中國電訊設備商華為副董事長孟晚舟，她之後獲准保釋，但要佩戴電子腳鐐接受監控，事件令中加關係急速降溫；其後加拿大前外交官康明凱及商人邁克爾先後在中國被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2498810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2498810&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=503bf660\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2498810</a>"},{"pid":"9aac1b6a9301b9d92d2a789c479011ee57500bdc","tid":2070391,"uid":153151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}